<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer11228990874605632803">A groundbreaking work of feminist history and theory analyzing the complex relations between various forms of oppression. <i>Ain&apos;t I a Woman</i> examines the impact of sexism on black women during slavery, the historic devaluation of black womanhood, black male sexism, racism within the recent women&apos;s movement, and black women&apos;s involvement with feminism.</span>
  <span id="freeText11228990874605632803" style="display:none">A groundbreaking work of feminist history and theory analyzing the complex relations between various forms of oppression. <i>Ain't I a Woman</i> examines the impact of sexism on black women during slavery, the historic devaluation of black womanhood, black male sexism, racism within the recent women's movement, and black women's involvement with feminism.</span>
