<a href="/questions/1841704-hi-i-am-a-white-woman-but-i-am-educated">Hi! I am a white woman but I am educated on the general concept of &quot;white feminism&quot;. Does this book go more in-depth with examples or is it a better read for people with no knowledge about the topic whatsoever? If so, does anyone have other recommendations that are still an &quot;easy&quot; read for a non-english-speaker (with adhd lol)?</a>
</div>
